description: This too is a hand-painted painting of mine that was then digitized and reworked with old-school effects. a dark piece of my soul is represented here. Sometimes I have the feeling that I am creating some kind of micro-currency and delving into my self as if it were an unexplored gold mine. But I often meet dark creatures, this is my art MINER who instead of gold fever has crypto fever, and digs every day like an ancient tireless creature
